":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:32:45.000Z","msg":"首先返九點做到十二點之後就倒數返九點<br />\n咁就唔洗食午餐<br />\n基本上就不斷loop<br />\n又可以做野 又可以唔洗食野<br />\n用盡一生幫公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0578516ae6eeef55153e2faa9f7b3f0dbe3ef503","tid":2224050,"uid":207462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T19:06:02.000Z","msg":"有咩好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天能個概念就係<br />\n已經發生咗既事係不能改變<br />\n未來不能夠改變過去<br />\n但過去作出決定會決定未來<br />\n<br />\n如果過去已經不同<br />\n你所存在嘅未來會消失<br />\n喺未來呢個時間點嘅你會一齊灰飛煙滅"},{"pid":"f8de3b4f50ff1e5624e88d55148fd3ed1ca69546","tid":2224050,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfef669e4e2d998eb508125dda23bcbd1401cf9c","tid":2224050,"uid":136797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"逆行射精會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T00:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/10/085640_5fc943fe3b6344451cb8610c8c79d4eb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F10%2F085640_5fc943fe3b6344451cb8610c8c79d4eb.gif&h=8472edb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d1637fa6be634e016dabf39c71d3310e31f4c70","tid":2224050,"uid":150021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"放工做唔哂，你逆時返去啲野只會由做左一半變返做未開始做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}